      <!-- START THE FEATURETTES -->

      <hr class="featurette-divider" id="how">

      <div class="featurette">
        <img class="featurette-image pull-right" src="../images/petri_signup.jpg">
        <h2 class="featurette-heading">Step 1: <span class="muted">Sign-up</span></h2>
        <p class="lead">Group leaders first create a personal account, which triggers automatic generation of a lab account. Members then link to their lab account via their group leader's email address. You're ready to begin.</p>
      </div>

      <hr class="featurette-divider">

      <div class="featurette">
        <img class="featurette-image pull-left" src="../images/petri_initial.jpg">
        <h2 class="featurette-heading">Step 2: <span class="muted"> Initial catalog</span></h2>
        <p class="lead">Establish a location code in your lab. Take one day off to perform an inventory together. Add only what you want to track. Catalog anything. Catalog everything.</p>
      </div>

      <hr class="featurette-divider">

      <div class="featurette">
        <img class="featurette-image pull-right" src="../images/petri_steady.jpg">
        <h2 class="featurette-heading">Step 3: <span class="muted">Steady state</span></h2>
        <p class="lead">Labs can collectively maintain accurate inventories with only five minutes / member / day on Infinitory. Observe history and metrics on anything. Waste less. Do more.</p>
      </div>

      <hr class="featurette-divider">